id: pm-xspd
title: "Close the jscpd/CodeFactor sensitivity gap: minTokens 115 misses low-token table clones the CodeFactor bot still files"
description: "Evidence 2026-07-11: pnpm lint:duplicates on main reports 0 clones (562 files, minLines 22 / minTokens 115) while CodeFactor filed GH-508 for a 28-line byte-identical object-literal table duplicated between create.ts:335-362 and update.ts:260-287. Short-identifier object rows stay under 115 tokens across 28 lines, so the zero-duplication gate from PR#506/pm-7wmq is structurally blind to table-shaped clones that CodeFactor's thresholds catch. Fixing pm-zuw8 clears this instance but not the class; result is recurring CodeFactor auto-issues despite a green local gate. Successor to closed parity item pm-6sqo."
